<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Seller Password Reset</title>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
				background-color: #f4f4f4;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
			}
			.container {
				max-width: 600px;
				margin: 20px auto;
				background-color: #ffffff;
				border-radius: 8px;
				overflow: hidden;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			}
			.header {
				background-color: #4a90e2;
				color: #ffffff;
				padding: 40px;
				text-align: center;
			}
			.header h1 {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 28px;
			}
			.content {
				padding: 40px;
				color: #333333;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			.content p {
				margin: 0 0 20px;
			}
			.otp-code {
				background-color: #f0f8ff;
				border: 1px dashed #4a90e2;
				color: #4a90e2;
				font-size: 36px;
				font-weight: bold;
				text-align: center;
				padding: 20px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				letter-spacing: 5px;
				margin: 30px 0;
			}
			.footer {
				background-color: #f4f4f4;
				color: #888888;
				padding: 20px;
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 12px;
			}
			.footer p {
				margin: 0;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="header">
				<h1>Seller Password Reset</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="content">
				<p>Dear <%= username %>,</p>
				<p>
					We received a request to reset the password for your seller account on E-Shop.<br />
					Please use the One-Time Password (OTP) below to securely reset your password:
				</p>

				<div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>

				<p>
					This OTP is valid for 10 minutes. If you did not initiate this request, please ignore this email and your seller account password will remain unchanged.
				</p>
				<p>
					For your security, never share this code with anyone. If you have any concerns about your account, please contact our support team immediately.
				</p>
				<p>Thank you for being a valued seller,<br />The E-Shop Team</p>
			</div>
			<div class="footer">
				<p>&copy; 2025 E-Shop. All rights reserved.</p>
				<p>123 Shopping Lane, Commerce City, 12345</p>
				<p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at 
					<a href="mailto:support@e-shop.com">support@e-shop.com</a>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
